<description-of-drawings>
<p id="p-0001" num="0001"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>1</b></figref> is a top, front, left perspective view of an ear wax remover with camera, shown assembled in a first configuration;</p>
<p id="p-0002" num="0002"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>2</b></figref> is a bottom, rear, left perspective view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0003" num="0003"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>3</b></figref> is a front elevation view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0004" num="0004"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>4</b></figref> is a rear elevation view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0005" num="0005"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>5</b></figref> is a left side elevation view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0006" num="0006"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>6</b></figref> is a right side elevation view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0007" num="0007"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>7</b></figref> is a top plan view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0008" num="0008"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>8</b></figref> is a bottom plan view thereof;</p>
<p id="p-0009" num="0009"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>9</b></figref> is a top, front, left perspective view of the ear wax remover with camera of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>1</b></figref>. shown assembled in condition of use for clarity of disclosure;</p>
<p id="p-0010" num="0010"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>10</b></figref> is a top, front, left perspective view of the ear wax remover with camera of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>1</b></figref>. shown exploded in condition of use for clarity of disclosure; and,</p>
<p id="p-0011" num="0011"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>11</b></figref> is a top, front, left perspective view of the ear wax remover with camera of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. <b>1</b></figref>. shown exploded in a second configuration.</p>
<p id="p-0012" num="0012">The broken lines in the drawings illustrate the portions of the ear wax remover with camera, which form no part of the claimed design.</p>
</description-of-drawings>
